{"tid":200203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同樣受肉芽(keloid)困擾多年？","createTime":"2017-04-13T18:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T07:30:17.000Z","uid":105596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2343c4f18fbaf3d2370846f3e39c7d3260a8fb","tid":200203,"uid":105596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:04:29.000Z","msg":"我好細個就開始個身就有幾噠凸起嘅肉芽<br />\n隨年齡增長有發大到 覺得好肉酸<br />\n成日唔想比人望到 尤其另一半好怕對方介意<br />\n啲人話係傷口傷理得唔好 疤痕組織增生而成<br />\n我睇遭醫生話好難搞 佢建議唔好理佢話有機會整完再生番 甚至更大<br />\n但我真係覺得好辛苦 有時好痕同痛 <br />\n由細到大都唔敢著背心泳衣 好多衫著唔到<br />\n我好怕會再發大<br />\n有無人做過手術/打針整走過 可以分享下？<br />\n<br />\n類似咁 ：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4t1wX5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4t1wX5X.jpg&h=8dbaff2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7g5TrOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7g5TrOu.jpg&h=bbef6f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c277370987c80ae8ca341657d11253813eebd76b","tid":200203,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:10:05.000Z","msg":"樓主係絲？<br />\n因為肉芽發生係女仔身上比較多<br />\n有同事都生過, 聽佢講做冷凍治療會醫好的"},{"pid":"9977d08e7eb192058bbe63cc10a84c9dbbba7347","tid":200203,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T23:16:34.000Z","msg":"dio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9415a36e47e22a69ee2591d8aa121f409a2587","tid":200203,"uid":89917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}